{"type": "article", "id": 6330, "title": "Sally 桌椅& Molly 储物架", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-16T07:40:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234337watkcGQMFJbSZhHg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在今年的科隆国际家具展上，日本设计师 Jin Kuramoto 发布了自有品牌 Matsuso T 旗下两个系列的新品，Sally 桌椅以及 Molly 储物架。Jin Kuramoto 与日本的工匠师傅合作，使用传统的木工技术，选择枫树材质进行制作。Sally 椅子有着平缓圆润的椅背，Jin Kuramoto 将 Sally 称作是用最少的元素完成一个稳固结构的桌椅。木制的储物架被一个织物包裹的软垫门覆盖，选用深浅不一的织物面料营造出层次感。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234334eKN3tmTLvid6GhIy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234335De2sQ3YX18kAVPyO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234335gfzhoWt93YMAG1iQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234336jAzDkMsKPHGX58L9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234336ACyHJPIv0sTVb4RX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}